Without Inbuilt (Two Pointer â€“ Best for Interview)
public class PalindromeCheck {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String s = "madam";
        boolean isPalindrome = true;

        int start = 0;
        int end = s.length() - 1;

        while (start < end) {
            if (s.charAt(start) != s.charAt(end)) {
                isPalindrome = false;
                break;
            }
            start++;
            end--;
        }

        System.out.println(isPalindrome);
    }
}

Time Complexity

â¡ï¸ O(n)

ğŸ’¾ Space Complexity

â¡ï¸ O(1)

